column2: SELECT g.specObjID,g.ra, g.dec, s.z, g.psfMag_g-g.extinction_g AS psf_mag_g,  g.psfMag_r-g.extinction_r AS psf_mag_r,  g.psfMag_i-g.extinction_i AS psf_mag_i,  g.psfMag_z-g.extinction_z AS psf_mag_z, g.cModelMag_g-g.extinction_g AS cmodel_mag_g,  g.cModelMag_r-g.extinction_r AS cmodel_mag_r,  g.cModelMag_i-g.extinction_i AS cmodel_mag_i,  g.cModelMag_z-g.extinction_z AS cmodel_mag_z  FROM Galaxy AS g JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON g.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE s.class = &&& AND s.sciencePrimary=# AND s.z># AND s.z<# AND g.ra > # and g.ra < # AND g.dec > # and g.dec < #
